snippet.title: Wise Kahlil Gibran Quotes On Life, Love And Marriage That Will Make You Think
snippet.description:
Wise Kahlil Gibran Quotes On Life, Love And Marriage That Will Make You Think. These are vivid sayings and quotes from Kahlil Gibran. The best quotes and aphorisms of Kahlil Gibran that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Mark Twain are definitely worth your time.

Gibran Khalil Gibran, usually referred to in English as Kahlil Gibran, was a Lebanese-American writer, poet and visual artist, also considered a philosopher although he himself rejected the title.
